{
  "stem": "20686.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, it's-- it's nearly 50 years, 60 years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not anymore the same man, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I-- it's difficult for me to go back and-- and respond to it question like this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It looked-- I thought it's one of the biggest cities in the world, you know, because I've never been anywhere else.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a dirty city full of smoke, a poor city, hardworking people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was life.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were beautiful gardens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, Jews had no access to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wouldn't let us in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it-- it really sort of-- it didn't have any specific character, like any other cities, like Warsaw, or Krakow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was-- it seems to me that in the beginning of-- of-- when Lodz was built, some-- a few people came and throw a heap of bricks into the sky, and wherever they fell down, there was a house.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was nothing-- nothing special.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very vibrant, very vibrant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we had-- we had libraries, and theater, and orchestra, and music.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the-- the desire to know, to understand, to be part of the-- of the universal knowledge of this big cosmic culture amongst young people is beyond comprehension, beyond.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had no schools.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They could not go to schools.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Universities were prohibited.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "High schools were only for the rich.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I could never-- I-- as far as I can remember, girls, instead of bags of this-- bags they were here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What do they call it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forgot the name of those-- those, they-- they under their arm was a book.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And boys had books.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when they got together, the first question is, what are you reading now?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And how do you respond to-- to so-and-so?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
